<section class="sh-section sh-bleed">
  <div class="sh-container">
    <div class="sh-center"><div class="sh-eyebrow">FAQ</div><h2 class="sh-h2">Before you start the system</h2></div>
    <div class="accordion" style="max-width:880px;margin:30px auto 0;">
      <details><summary>Is Shadeless a whitening product?</summary><div class="content">No. Shadeless is not about changing your natural skin tone. It is designed to help skin look clearer, smoother, more even, and more refined across every skin tone.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Do I need all three steps?</summary><div class="content">The full system is recommended because each step has a distinct role: prepare, optimize, and enhance.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can I use this morning and night?</summary><div class="content">Yes, follow the product directions for each step. During the day, always finish with sunscreen.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can sensitive skin use it?</summary><div class="content">If your skin is sensitive, patch test first and introduce the system gradually. Discontinue use if irritation occurs.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Do I need sunscreen?</summary><div class="content">Yes. Use sunscreen every morning as the final step of your daytime routine.</div></details>
    </div>
    <div class="sh-center" style="margin-top:30px;"><a class="sh-button sh-button--secondary" href="/pages/faq">Read the FAQ</a></div>
  </div>
</section>
